    <Replace Tag="LOC_CIV6_AI_COPILOT_TOOLTIP_SYNC_TURN" Language="en_US">
      <Text>Summarize core turn information for city, technology, civic, resource, and public diplomacy analysis.</Text>
    </Replace>
    <Replace Tag="LOC_CIV6_AI_COPILOT_TOOLTIP_SYNC_TURN" Language="zh_Hans_CN">
      <Text>汇总本回合基础情报，适合城市、科技、市政、资源与公开外交等常规分析。</Text>
    </Replace>

    <Replace Tag="LOC_CIV6_AI_COPILOT_TOOLTIP_SYNC_MAP" Language="en_US">
      <Text>Update revealed and currently visible map information for settlement, scouting, naval, frontline, and war planning.</Text>
    </Replace>
    <Replace Tag="LOC_CIV6_AI_COPILOT_TOOLTIP_SYNC_MAP" Language="zh_Hans_CN">
      <Text>更新已揭示与当前可见地图情报，适合定居、侦察、海军、前线与战争判断。</Text>
    </Replace>

    <Replace Tag="LOC_CIV6_AI_COPILOT_TOOLTIP_AUTO_SYNC" Language="en_US">
      <Text>When enabled, prepares one turn brief at the start of the local player's turn. Off by default.</Text>
    </Replace>
    <Replace Tag="LOC_CIV6_AI_COPILOT_TOOLTIP_AUTO_SYNC" Language="zh_Hans_CN">
      <Text>开启后，仅在本地玩家回合开始时自动汇总一次本回合情报。默认关闭。</Text>
    </Replace>

    <Replace Tag="LOC_CIV6_AI_COPILOT_TOOLTIP_SYNC_CITIES" Language="en_US">
      <Text>Summarize city population, housing, amenities, districts, yields, and current production for city-by-city planning.</Text>
    </Replace>
    <Replace Tag="LOC_CIV6_AI_COPILOT_TOOLTIP_SYNC_CITIES" Language="zh_Hans_CN">
      <Text>汇总城市人口、住房、宜居度、区域、产出与当前生产，用于逐城规划。</Text>
    </Replace>

    <Replace Tag="LOC_CIV6_AI_COPILOT_TOOLTIP_SYNC_UNITS" Language="en_US">
      <Text>Summarize your units and currently visible foreign units for scouting, defense, redeployment, and war assessment.</Text>
    </Replace>
    <Replace Tag="LOC_CIV6_AI_COPILOT_TOOLTIP_SYNC_UNITS" Language="zh_Hans_CN">
      <Text>汇总己方单位与当前可见外方单位，用于侦察、防守、调兵与战事判断。</Text>
    </Replace>

    <Replace Tag="LOC_CIV6_AI_COPILOT_TOOLTIP_SYNC_RESOURCES" Language="en_US">
      <Text>Summarize strategic resources, luxuries, and stockpiles for upgrades, upkeep, trades, and amenities.</Text>
    </Replace>
    <Replace Tag="LOC_CIV6_AI_COPILOT_TOOLTIP_SYNC_RESOURCES" Language="zh_Hans_CN">
      <Text>汇总战略资源、奢侈品与库存状态，用于升级、维护、交易和宜居度判断。</Text>
    </Replace>

    <Replace Tag="LOC_CIV6_AI_COPILOT_TOOLTIP_SYNC_TECH_CIVICS" Language="en_US">
      <Text>Summarize technology, civics, eurekas, and inspirations for route planning and timing decisions.</Text>
    </Replace>
    <Replace Tag="LOC_CIV6_AI_COPILOT_TOOLTIP_SYNC_TECH_CIVICS" Language="zh_Hans_CN">
      <Text>汇总科技、市政、尤里卡与鼓舞进度，用于路线规划和关键时机判断。</Text>
    </Replace>

    <Replace Tag="LOC_CIV6_AI_COPILOT_TOOLTIP_SYNC_GOVERNMENT" Language="en_US">
      <Text>Summarize government, policy slots, and active policies for card changes, timing windows, and strategic pacing.</Text>
    </Replace>
    <Replace Tag="LOC_CIV6_AI_COPILOT_TOOLTIP_SYNC_GOVERNMENT" Language="zh_Hans_CN">
      <Text>汇总当前政体、政策槽与已插政策，用于换卡、产能爆发和战略节奏规划。</Text>
    </Replace>

    <Replace Tag="LOC_CIV6_AI_COPILOT_TOOLTIP_SYNC_DIPLOMACY" Language="en_US">
      <Text>Summarize met civilizations, public relationships, and visible diplomatic information for trade, alliance, and war-risk assessment.</Text>
    </Replace>
    <Replace Tag="LOC_CIV6_AI_COPILOT_TOOLTIP_SYNC_DIPLOMACY" Language="zh_Hans_CN">
      <Text>汇总已遇见文明、公开关系与可见外交信息，用于交易、结盟和战争风险判断。</Text>
    </Replace>

    <Replace Tag="LOC_CIV6_AI_COPILOT_TOOLTIP_FORCE_FULL" Language="en_US">
      <Text>Rebuild the full briefing context for first use, version changes, diagnostics, or several topics needing updates.</Text>
    </Replace>
