    </Replace>

    <Replace Tag="LOC_CIV6_AI_COPILOT_TOOLTIP_ICON_POSITION" Language="en_US">
      <Text>ICON_POSITION. Neutral marker; compact, but less distinctive.</Text>
    </Replace>
    <Replace Tag="LOC_CIV6_AI_COPILOT_TOOLTIP_ICON_POSITION" Language="zh_Hans_CN">
      <Text>ICON_POSITION。中性定位标记，体积克制，但辨识度偏弱。</Text>
    </Replace>

    <Replace Tag="LOC_CIV6_AI_COPILOT_TOOLTIP_ICON_QUEUE" Language="en_US">
      <Text>ICON_QUEUE. Related to planning, but close to production queue language.</Text>
    </Replace>
    <Replace Tag="LOC_CIV6_AI_COPILOT_TOOLTIP_ICON_QUEUE" Language="zh_Hans_CN">
      <Text>ICON_QUEUE。偏向规划语义，但容易联想到生产队列。</Text>
    </Replace>

    <Replace Tag="LOC_CIV6_AI_COPILOT_TOOLTIP_ICON_GREAT_PERSON" Language="en_US">
      <Text>ICON_GREAT_PERSON. Human-advisor feel; may overlap with Great People.</Text>
    </Replace>
    <Replace Tag="LOC_CIV6_AI_COPILOT_TOOLTIP_ICON_GREAT_PERSON" Language="zh_Hans_CN">
      <Text>ICON_GREAT_PERSON。有副官感，但可能与伟人入口混淆。</Text>
    </Replace>

    <Replace Tag="LOC_CIV6_AI_COPILOT_TOOLTIP_ICON_GENERIC_MODIFIER" Language="en_US">
      <Text>ICON_STATS_GENERIC_MODIFIER. Analytical and unobtrusive; less ceremonial.</Text>
    </Replace>
    <Replace Tag="LOC_CIV6_AI_COPILOT_TOOLTIP_ICON_GENERIC_MODIFIER" Language="zh_Hans_CN">
      <Text>ICON_STATS_GENERIC_MODIFIER。偏分析与状态提示，存在感较弱。</Text>
    </Replace>

    <Replace Tag="LOC_CIV6_AI_COPILOT_TOOLTIP_ICON_REPORTS" Language="en_US">
      <Text>LaunchBar_Hook_Reports. Closest to a briefing or report entry.</Text>
    </Replace>
    <Replace Tag="LOC_CIV6_AI_COPILOT_TOOLTIP_ICON_REPORTS" Language="zh_Hans_CN">
      <Text>LaunchBar_Hook_Reports。最接近战情简报与情报报告语义。</Text>
    </Replace>

    <Replace Tag="LOC_CIV6_AI_COPILOT_TOOLTIP_ICON_GREAT_WORKS" Language="en_US">
      <Text>LaunchBar_Hook_GreatWorks. Book-like silhouette; readable but cultural.</Text>
    </Replace>
    <Replace Tag="LOC_CIV6_AI_COPILOT_TOOLTIP_ICON_GREAT_WORKS" Language="zh_Hans_CN">
      <Text>LaunchBar_Hook_GreatWorks。书册轮廓清晰，但文化意味更强。</Text>
    </Replace>

    <Replace Tag="LOC_CIV6_AI_COPILOT_TOOLTIP_ICON_LAUNCH_GREAT_PEOPLE" Language="en_US">
      <Text>LaunchBar_Hook_GreatPeople. Advisor-like figure; possible overlap with Great People.</Text>
    </Replace>
    <Replace Tag="LOC_CIV6_AI_COPILOT_TOOLTIP_ICON_LAUNCH_GREAT_PEOPLE" Language="zh_Hans_CN">
      <Text>LaunchBar_Hook_GreatPeople。人物感强，但可能与伟人入口混淆。</Text>
    </Replace>

    <Replace Tag="LOC_CIV6_AI_COPILOT_TOOLTIP_ICON_TRADE" Language="en_US">
      <Text>LaunchBar_Hook_Trade. Strategic overview tone; less tied to an assistant.</Text>
    </Replace>
    <Replace Tag="LOC_CIV6_AI_COPILOT_TOOLTIP_ICON_TRADE" Language="zh_Hans_CN">
      <Text>LaunchBar_Hook_Trade。偏战略概览，但不直接表达副官。</Text>
    </Replace>

    <Replace Tag="LOC_CIV6_AI_COPILOT_TOOLTIP_ICON_WORLD_RANKINGS" Language="en_US">
